Privacy Policy
VVI is very interested in maintaining the privacy rights of our customers. VVI uses customer information internally for its own business purposes and never discloses customer information externally unless authorized to do so by the respective customer or as required by law. VVI also takes precautions to prevent unintended disclosure of customer information.
VVI will, from time to time, communicate with customers and prospective customers regarding VVI's own products and services.
Please report any privacy issues you may have to
support@vvi.com
where we will give your input prompt consideration.
For additional legal information please consult:
Legal
